title: 11/01: Start or Sit (AFC); Players Trending Up (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Let's talk about a few studs with potentially tough matchups (1:30) and whether there is any hesitation to start them. Then we've got a bunch of players who are trending up lately (10:00) like Mitchell Trubisky, Latavius Murray, Lamar Miller and Tyler Boyd. Are these guys legit or are they sell high candidates? ... News and notes (20:30) and a Ben Roethlisberger vs. Matthew Stafford debate (25:00) ... PIT-BAL (29:03), CHI-BUF (37:02), NYJ-MIA (42:06), HOU-DEN (48:00), KC-CLE (53:00), GB-NE (56:30) ...
